Global Outdoor Fire Hydrant Market Insights
Outdoor Fire Hydrant Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Outdoor Fire Hydrant Market Overview
The global outdoor fire hydrant market is experiencing significant growth, with the market size valued at USD 2.6 billion in 2024 and expected to reach USD 3.2 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 5.5%. The increasing demand for advanced fire safety solutions, coupled with stringent fire safety regulations in urban and industrial areas, is a key factor driving market growth. Additionally, the growing focus on improving infrastructure and the rising awareness about fire hazards in residential and commercial buildings further contribute to the market expansion. Major manufacturers are focusing on technological advancements, such as corrosion-resistant and easy-to-maintain fire hydrants, which is anticipated to further boost market demand.

